Interface IndexedSet<T>

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.Collection<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Set<T>
public interface IndexedSet<T>
extends java.util.Set<T>

Interface describing set that keeps elements in the insertion order and whose elements can be reached with indices.
